asset.title: Ernie Paniccioli's 70th Birthday Party | Steve Madden Music
asset.description:
Ernie Paniccioli is the eyes of old-school hip-hop thanks to his timeless photos of iconic artists. 

The photographer, artist, author and activist has been bringing us photos of hip-hop's most iconic names such as The Notorious B.I.G., Slick Rick, Grandmaster Flash, Doug E. Fresh, Ice Cube, Queen Latifah, Public Enemy & Salt-N-Pepa, to this generation's heavy hitters like Jay-Z, Eminem & Lauryn Hill, just to name a few.

He showed pride for his passion, his family, and his Cree roots during the celebration between performances from Melle Mel, Parrish from EPMD, and many more. Hip hop’s finest artists and friends all came to celebrate.

Steve Madden Music was on-site talking with some of Ernie’s best friends and old school hip-hop greats.

#STEVEMADDENMUSIC
